aAn2015\">{{cite web|title=2015 Guest - Matthew Mercer |url=http://www.sacanime.com/?page_id=9087 |website=SacAnime |accessdate=August 17, 2016 |url-status=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012024135/http://www.sacanime.com/?page_id=9087 |archivedate=October 12, 2014 }}</ref><ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|08|06|format=y}} || ''[[Tales of Xillia]]'' || Alvin || || Tweet<ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|10|25|format=y}} || ''[[Batman: Arkham Origins]]'' || [[Anarky]] || || Press<ref name=\"SaAn2015\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|11|15|format=y}} || ''[[Knack (video game)|Knack]]'' || Gundahar || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|12|19|format=y}} || ''[[R\u00e9publique (video game)|R\u00e9publique]]'' || Prizrak || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2014|03|11|format=y}} ||  ''[[Hearthstone]]'' || [[Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne#Plot|Rexxar]], others ||  || Press,<ref name=\"SaAn2015\"/> Tweet<ref>{{cite tweet | title=All you @PlayHearthstone players, keep an ear out for me in the new Blackrock Mountain Expansion as Grim Guzzler, Nefarian, & Ragnaros! |date = April 2, 2015 | accessdate = September 27, 2015 |author = Matthew Mercer | number =583722738537201664 |user = matthewmercer}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2014|03|18|format=y}} || ''[[Metal Gear Solid V: Ground Zeroes]]'' || The Eye, Prisoner 12282 ||  || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2014|09|09|format=y}} || ''[[Destiny (video game)|Destiny]]'' || Guardian: Human Male || || <ref>{{cite web|last1=Kuchera|first1=Ben|title=How the voices behind your favorite games and shows are re-inventing live D&D|url=http://www.polygon.com/features/2016/1/11/10589378/how-the-voices-behind-your-favorite-games-and-shows-are-re-inventing|website=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]]|accessdate=February 15, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite video| title = Destiny \u2013 End Credits \u2013 IGN Video| url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2014/09/11/destiny-end-credits| work=IGN Video| date= September 11, 2014\n| accessdate= De