imation-reveals-black-butler-book-of-circus-and-book-of-murder-anime-casts-release-dates/.98650|work=[[Anime News Network]] |accessdate=5 May 2017|date=February 13, 2016 | first=Crystalyn | last=Hodgkins}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016|06|03|format=y}} || ''[[Fairy Tail]]'' || Silver Fullbuster || || <ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-06-03/fairy-tail-english-dub-casts-matthew-mercer-ricco-fajardo-jeremy-schwartz/.102792 | title=Fairy Tail English Dub Casts Matthew Mercer, Ricco Fajardo, Jeremy Schwartz | work=[[Anime News Network]] | date=June 3, 2016 | accessdate=February 15, 2017 |  first=Karen | last=Ressler}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016|12|27|format=y}} || ''[[Sengoku Basara: End of Judgement]]'' || Mitsunari Ishida ||  || <ref name=\"SB: EoJ ep1\">{{cite episode | series = Sengoku Basara | serieslink = Sengoku Basara: End of Judgement | title = Rift | airdate = December 27, 2016 | network = [[Funimation]] | episodelink=List of Sengoku Basara: End of Judgement#Episode list | number=1 | time=Closing credits}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017-19 ||''[[JoJo's Bizarre Adventure (2012 TV series)|JoJo's Bizarre Adventure]]'' || [[Stardust Crusaders#Jotaro Kujo|Jotaro Kujo]] ||[[JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Stardust Crusaders|Stardust Crusaders]], [[JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Diamond Is Unbreakable|Diamond Is Unbreakable]] \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2014/06/23-1/crunchyroll-to-stream-english-dub-of-jojos-bizarre-adventure-stardust-crusaders|title=Crunchyroll to Stream English Dub of \"JOJO\u2019S BIZARRE ADVENTURE: STARDUST CRUSADERS\"|last=Macias|first=Patrick|publisher=[[Crunchyroll]] | date=June 23, 2014|accessdate=June 24, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2017|format=y}}\u201319 || ''[[Dragon Ball Super]]'' || Hit || Funimation dub  || <ref>{{cite news | last=Moore | first=Lauren | title=Dragon Ball Super - Universe 6 & 7 tournament English cast announcement - Funimation - Blog!|url=https://www.funimation.com/blog/2017/08/25/dragon-ball