dy]]'' \u2013 Library Staffer, additional voices\n* ''[[Sword Art Online]]'' \u2013 Grimlock, Lind, Kunimittz, Seijiro Kikuoka/Chrysheight\n| 2014 ||''[[Sword Art Online II]]'' || Seijiro Kikuoka || || {{cn|reason=BTVA does not confirm this role, need another source}}\n* ''[[Tenkai Knights]]'' \u2013 Zephyrus\n* ''[[Trigun]]'' \u2013 Additional voices\n* ''[[Zetman]]'' \u2013 Hayami, Superhero Alphas, Agou Shimura (Ep. 4), Shuu Isono/Sea Lice EVOL (Eps. 4\u20137)\n{{Div col end}}\n--->\n\n====Animation====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of voice performances in animation\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Source\n|-\n| {{dts|2011|07|29|format=y}}\u201312 || ''[[ThunderCats (2011 TV series)|ThunderCats]]'' || [[Tygra]] || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2013|07|13|format=y}} ||  ''[[Beware the Batman]]'' || Ice Pick Joe || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2015|07|25|format=y}} ||  ''[[DC Super Friends]]'' || [[Superman]], [[Two-Face]] || || <ref>{{cite episode | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YUvo3wr3C_o | title=The Cape and the Clown | accessdate=July 31, 2015 | number=1 | publication-date=May 4, 2015 | series=DC Super Friends | serieslink=DC Super Friends | time=Closing credits | via=YouTube}}</ref><ref>{{cite episode | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YUvo3wr3C_o | title= The Brave & The Bald | accessdate=July 31, 2015 | number=2 | publication-date=May 4, 2015 | series=DC Super Friends | serieslink=DC Super Friends | time=Closing credits | via=YouTube}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2015|09|format=y}} ||  ''[[Wabbit (TV series)|Wabbit]]'' || Bigfoot || <!-- main char --> || Tweet<ref>{{cite tweet | title=Proud to be playing Bigfoot in the new series \"Wabbit\", premiering Monday on #CartoonNetwork! |date = September 19, 2015 | accessdate = September 27, 2015 |author = Matthew Mercer | number =645418910750105601 |user = matthewmercer}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2016|09|26|format=y}} || ''[[Regu